text: Rodolfo Grazzini (born 3 June 1945) is an Argentine equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Argentina Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
